Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Martial law in Poland
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043wt32
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 20 Dec 1981
US administration warns Soviets over martial law in Poland - but accepts its own impotence to intervene. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less